h1 FreeCodeCamp API Basejump: URL Shortener Microservice

h3 User stories:
ul 
    li I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.
    li When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.

h3 Example creation usage:
a(href='https://camper-api-project-aboorde.c9users.io/new?url=https://www.google.com') https://camper-api-project-aboorde.c9users.io/new?url=https://www.google.com
br
br
a(href='https://camper-api-project-aboorde.c9users.io/new?url=http://foo.com:80') https://camper-api-project-aboorde.c9users.io/new?url=http://foo.com:80

h3 Example creation output
code { "original_url":"http://foo.com:80", "short_url":"https://little-url.herokuapp.com/8170" }

h3 Usage:
a(href='https://little-url.herokuapp.com/2871') https://little-url.herokuapp.com/2871

h4 Will redirect to:
a(href='https://www.google.com/') https://www.google.com/